{"tid":1186956,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[運動科學系列] 增肌及減肥篇","createTime":"2019-06-05T09:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T11:28:10.000Z","uid":256501,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"474921a5ea44abff58b1014d8c4c43c0e43bd8a8","tid":1186956,"uid":256501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:46:29.000Z","msg":"宗旨：<br />\n大家交流多D，講多D，等唔識野的人(包括我)可以學多D。<br />\n<br />\n-------<br />\n我諗有唔少人都聽過用 1/2/4 呢個 tempo 去舉鐵，即：<br />\n1 - Concentric (收縮)<br />\n2- Isometric (hold住)<br />\n4 - Eccentric (放鬆)<br />\n咁樣不單會刺激到最多muscle fibre，<br />\n而且，以呢個tempo去舉8-12下，可以延長肌肉受刺激的時間，最有利於增肌。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇用開咩tempo去舉，或者有冇其他大路的tempo可以介紹？<br />\n係咪用不同的tempo去對應不同的目的？"},{"pid":"ed6173adb5ba0daa481e61ddbf3277813202bed6","tid":1186956,"uid":186628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主 長知識了"}]}